text: Josef Nüsser (born 13 July 1931) was a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
